<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Cristoff, als wir euch nehst
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Smyds von Rystelbach
            und seins suns, des C. Pelhofers, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, <expan>arme<ex>n</ex>leute</expan> wegen, also hat der
                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Pelhofer <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vor uns czu den <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> behabt,
            daz der <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Smyd und sein sun hinter im gesessen sein und die
            besliesz mit tür und tor. Hyrümb <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                <expan>dyeselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> armlewte ledig lassen wöllet
              <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii post
              <expan>co<ex>n</ex>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>ionem</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Pauli.</ab>
